# PCF Souvenirs — internal enterprise timesheet app
# Matches Angular's own minimum browser floor (Chrome/Edge 107, Firefox 104, Safari/iOS 16).
# Keeping the floor below CSS nesting support (Chrome 112) ensures Angular's build tool
# un-nests DaisyUI 5's CSS output correctly rather than validating and dropping rules.
Chrome >= 107
ChromeAndroid >= 107
Edge >= 107
Firefox >= 104
FirefoxAndroid >= 104
Safari >= 16
iOS >= 16
